<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[المحراث]</span>: محراث الحرب: ما يهيجها.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">والمحراث:</span> ما تُحرك به النار.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
